sequenceDiagram
  participant Browser
  participant Shell as Shell index.html
  participant Map as Import Map
  participant App as Micro‑Frontend

  Browser->>Shell: Load index.html
  Shell-->>Map: Define mappings (e.g. @owner-portal/web → URL)
  Browser->>Shell: Execute root-config
  Shell->>Browser: registerApplication(activeWhen)
  Browser->>Map: Resolve @module name to URL
  Browser->>App: import(URL)
  App-->>Browser: Exports lifecycles/bootstrap
  Browser->>App: call bootstrap → mount

